## The Big Picture Pipeline

By decoupling the backend from the front-end parser, your single language architecture can now handle multiple targets flawlessly:

```
                  ┌───> [ CodeGenerator ] ────> PUSH 14, STORE x (Machine Stack)
[ Source AST ] ───┤
                  └───> [ EnglishTranspiler ] ─> "Assign to variable x..." (Plain English)

```
